        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>What is the best book you've ever read and why?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 80 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>The best book I've ever read is a classic, Harry Potter. I've grew up with the saga, since I was a child until now. This made all of my childhood and a part of my teenage.</p>
                <p>J.K. Rowling is a very good writter. She's able to find the good words to describe an amazing landscapes and a wonderful universe with strange creatures  where the magic is daily.</p>
                <p>In addition, 8 movies were shot, and this makes the saga and the characters more real. It's rare when the movie are to the novel's level, but here it a success.</p>
            </div>
